data.description: Location, Location, Location!!!! MOTIVATED SELLER-!!!  HOME IS OCCUPIED DO WALK ANY PART OF THE PROPERTY WITHOUT AN APPOINTMENT! Nestled off the road among the trees with views of the Gorge, listen for the echoes of the Cuyahoga River from your new home!!!!  This 3-5 bedroom 3 full bath ecological retreat offers more on the inside than meets the eye. So much character of days gone by from the hardwood floors, to the dormers & built ins, to all the nooks & crannies. Hardwood floors in the living room with wood burn FP.  The dining area leads the kitchen with a step down to eating area with picturesque views & access to the 2 car attached garage. 2 first floor BDRMS & a full bath complete the first floor.  Upstairs you will find a master BDRM suite with a full bath & sitting areas. The lower level consists of 2 BDRMS, a full bath, a dedicated laundry area, utility room, a large sunroom with vaulted ceilings & 4 sliding doors exiting to the nature reserve backyard.  The storage shed w/electric offers a full deck with panoramic views.  Some recent updates in the last year include:  new roof, hot water tank, range & double oven (all come with a transferable manufacturers warranty).  Furnace is 5 years new, AC 6 years new, gutters with leaf guard 4 years new.  Seller is offering a one year home warranty.  This home is tucked away yet close to all the things: Babb Run Bird & Wildlife Sanctuary, Cuyahoga Valley Natl Pk, the Pro-football Hall of Fame and more! HOME IS OCCUPIED!!
